==Bundles==
Magma Cap is not used in any [[bundles]].

==Tailoring==
Magma Cap is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create a [[Tailoring|Magenta Shirt]]. [[File:Magenta Shirt.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Magma Cap is not used in any [[quests]].

